Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:29.40,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}「你注意到了嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:36.12,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一邊輕聲說出來  一邊揮著小手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:44.27,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}想要讓這樣的每一天都持續下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:50.78,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}就把茶匙扔出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:59.76,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}掌管咖啡的神仙啊  總有一天我們會長大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.85,0:21:07.24,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}用白色的牛奶來  描繪出大家的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:14.99,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}掌管咖啡的神仙啊  總有一天我們會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:19.71,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}成為可愛的大人…雖然是這麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:25.40,ED2CHN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不過接下來的事情可就不知道咯！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------TXT----------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給大家看去露營時候的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拍了這麼多照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍的很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你拍的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個美麗的姑娘是誰呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.92,0:00:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是心愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.20,0:00:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的沒看出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也太驚訝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實看起來比較成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我可以拿走一張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃很有才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一張奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  連你們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃  這是照相機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露營時開始拍照之後就上癮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以讓我好好拍拍你們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在拍照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.83,0:02:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主題是  平時的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像往常一樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被這麼說反倒覺得有點難了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擺姿勢更有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我感到了很厲害的溫度差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我拍一下你們在說話時的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你總來搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  我只是在工作卻被批評了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個照片好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這種的怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跳的好累
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  不能一直這樣偷懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也來給我拍張照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很老練
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天做了保養
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為心愛的影響  目的已經開始跑偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有野性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍專注於拍照的智乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道背後有人照她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐的背影…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最佳鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼最佳鏡頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  要到打工的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗路  你沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.69,0:04:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我總是會忘記時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛讓她跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那麼執著於平時的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還專門把照相機帶到店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是在隱瞞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來告訴姐姐們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  被拍了奇怪的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一下子就能擺出表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}求刪…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要開始打掃店裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡樂的露營也結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要回歸為一名勞動者啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好意思說自己勞動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千夜要不要再喝一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀  恭敬不如從命啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡夾了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是探寶遊戲的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要找到寶物然後把其中一樣和自己的交換
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}對對  結束後是要把地圖藏在別的地方對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探寶遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道小鎮上到底藏著多少地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前找到過好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只和紗路找過一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個小鎮上…大家都玩過啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們下次一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把麻耶和惠叫來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作為姐姐會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  寶物都帶過來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者的斷劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像寶石一樣的扣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇難船隻的瓶裝船模
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不錯啊不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論哪個都能激起人的冒險慾望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帶了什麼過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用提比掉的毛做的提比分身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理世也來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她今天留下來看店所以今天才能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還要感謝理世呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然是第一次但是會努力引領大家前進的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還沒有找到過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.68,0:06:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得最開始是剛上初中的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對  就是那次遇到了智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  下一位  開始自我介紹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我是香風智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.10,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將來的夢想是成為出色的咖啡師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻耶  咖啡師是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我在遊戲和電影里見過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個把箭和石頭之類打出去的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是想打破人生的牆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是個很厲害的咖啡師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.24,0:07:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你來成為我們的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才我們找到了探寶遊戲的地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼突然幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要咖啡師的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是重要的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃加入到了隊伍中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有過這種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從那時開始關係就很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個奇怪的誤會真是抱歉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次的探寶遊戲那麼難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻耶立馬開始繞路走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠提議玩其他遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃說已經累了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底賴誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賴誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這次沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.47,0:08:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有姐姐在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛你是個路癡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好好看這個地圖就能到達的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這些圖全都拼湊起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  從而能夠得出的答案是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王冠  兔子  店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有名的帽子店…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.68,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是讓在甘兔庵吃豆沙水果涼粉是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害  不愧是心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人想不出這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是想吃豆沙水果涼粉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要證明心愛的想法是有多麼的膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們用一下秘密的通道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.26,0:09:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊更近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是在冒險一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以前尋寶的時候發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候被葉子封著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是近路但是過不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易來了一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.80,0:09:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡到了智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出場的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是咖啡師的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃你還有那種能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是他們捏造的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為在遇到我之前你還會那種魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡師是泡咖啡的職業啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻耶她們總是亂說  很脫線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個小鎮真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.31,0:10:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘是些想讓人繞路的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繞道的話就可以多玩會兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許她們倆剛和智乃見面的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想讓關係變得更好所以總是脫線呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這次想大家一起找到寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺公園那邊有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人都別偷懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好努力找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛也快來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這個是不是智乃說的帽子店的牌子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在盆栽箱的後面找到了一個寶箱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.81,0:11:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  你們還記得咱們是怎麼走到這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去熱愛了許多的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又稍微憎恨一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銘刻著靈魂的回憶和羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是  寶物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,側面有個新的地圖貼在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說怎麼這麼奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是知道的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是故意那麼說的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似在這個小洞的盡頭有著寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有小孩才進得去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.44,0:12:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉勉強強能進來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輕鬆輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛不會進不來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡只有被選中的霍比特人才能通過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在這裡和提比阻止追兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}妹妹們啊  踩著我的屍體前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩得真開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個神聖的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寶箱就藏著這裡的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就…就是這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是榮譽勳章！好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來有不少人來過這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…甘兔庵的打折券？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連捶肩券都有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs18}甘兔庵  9折優惠券
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs18}捶肩券  請珍惜地使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們三個  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不快點回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛就會一直在那裡等著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次的尋寶比以前的都要開心吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為心愛在的緣故吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點吃醋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對是你們的錯覺啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是霍比特一族的休息之地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算身體這麼大  內心還是小小的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內心小小的不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明心愛也變成霍比特人就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果心愛還是沒能完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,規則上能動寶箱的只有設置寶箱的本人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想再一次尋寶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過會兒跟智乃商量下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃會不會同意我的請求呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分的都是有趣的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是為什麼一有跟心愛扯上關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她因為生氣身子都在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…心愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我的錯拍出來的都是那種照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒在生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃理想中的姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.19,0:15:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這只吧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只不就是心愛麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然那張照片上的心愛的確看起來很有姐姐范
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想說的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還不夠格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒能成為合格的智乃的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能夠像照片這樣更加像個成熟的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.94,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能成為讓智乃引以為傲的姐姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我…就連讓智乃感到自豪都不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  智乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我一直覺得心愛來到這個小鎮真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛你這個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真敢扔啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一直都這麼自作主張地下定論…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因為這個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…你不是在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不告訴你呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一枕頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.21,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚有點喧囂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛這種程度比起安安靜靜的好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我意外地都習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照這麼下去還不得上房揭瓦總有一天會把店給拆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我店鬧拆了我就困擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也給我加把勁去讓生意更加興隆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是把「有著會說話的兔子的有趣咖啡店」作為賣點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會更有反響也說不定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的明白老夫的心情嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…不能看！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐寫給智乃的信？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「實際上  只要是心愛寄給我的照片就都是搞笑風格的」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「所以想麻煩你多發點普通的日常照…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為  為什麼要瞞著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果讓你知道這是給摩卡姐的照片的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定會去做酷酷的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一直都是自然的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是已經介意得不行了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個東西準備好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備OK的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們會不會高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探寶遊戲的地圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的寶物由初中生組藏好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的這個可是難度很高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.83,0:18:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…這個打折券能用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…是我努力做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請收下它！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情書？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛  理世  請把這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為之前看店的謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們幾個藏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次輪到我來看店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩位也去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是針對我們的挑戰狀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前只有我沒有通過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽  快看快看  寄過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.06,0:18:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛和智乃寄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不錯的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃  謝謝你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去很精神  媽媽我也就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.99,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  這個…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.46,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也看看心愛的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也遲遲不回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話  我可就要再回去見見她咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然呢  心愛送過來的照片全都很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也很喜歡這種的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過的還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個重要的通知要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為姐姐瞞著我要搶走智乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一個月內不會跟姐姐聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明沒那個打算的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛啊！！！！！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼大家  把得到的寶物拿出來看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個勳章…是我從小到大一直在收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  我就覺得理世肯定會選這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.13,0:21:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是麻耶放進去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是  芭蕾舞鞋的鑰匙圈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.15,0:22:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是希望你一直都能華麗地舞動起來的護身符哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就像芭蕾舞者那樣一直骨碌骨碌地迎客好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個讓人靜不下心來的咖啡店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是這個可愛的小小的書哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.11,0:22:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是青山小姐放進去的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能再跟大家一起玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢  紗路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.60,0:22:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了…真是讓人沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個奇怪的臉的人的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…不就是你麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Me？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個就是…我就是寶物的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不對  智乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是…不把店再弄熱鬧點的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.50,0:23:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都交給姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…心愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.61,0:23:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺好像聽到了什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒有說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心愛  聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才紗路她…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.69,0:23:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理  理世學姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  那個不都是怪千夜嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明在和小惠她們喝紅茶呢  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智乃要不要吃點餅乾？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…我開動了哦
